  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/bcb3613488ad18b7c57733143b3cb379.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>Sky Oceans: Wings For Hire is a homage to JRPG classics! Set in the open skies, experience adrenaline-filled turn-based dogfights as you take the role of captain and unite a party of rag-tag sky pirates setting upon an unforgettable, touching journey.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/c9f117a3c6ce9ee9a4b0ad1900cb1df1.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Relive the charm of classic RPGs with a touching story about the search for purpose. Take the role of Glenn Windwalker as you assemble your team of sky pirates and fight against the 'Alliance'. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/deaaec41b49ed07c45c1129bfe827bee.poster.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/deaaec41b49ed07c45c1129bfe827bee.webm?t=1760535466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/deaaec41b49ed07c45c1129bfe827bee.mp4?t=1760535466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/7217235bbf0c22f90e251865171a9d17.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Fight adversaries within the open skies in strategic turn-based dog fights. Tactically plan attacks and adapt your strategy to the ever-changing scenarios! Unlock new special moves & equipped your team with the best possible chance of victory! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/b3f365e0f77a84113bcb3011e4637766.poster.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/b3f365e0f77a84113bcb3011e4637766.webm?t=1760535466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/b3f365e0f77a84113bcb3011e4637766.mp4?t=1760535466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/055b76d43973921bf799198c29d2df7c.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Assemble a party of rag tag air pirates and upgrade airships with new special abilities as you progress through a winding narrative! Manage resources and expand your airship departments strategically. Do you have what it takes to be captain?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/73fe08c89feec5cc9524e40487e2895d.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=332 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/d275715fb85d5cc3c825b115fcc62fd1.avif?t=1760535466\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>Stunning Studio Ghibli-inspired visuals make for diverse environments and memorable character design. Discover new towns, cultures and help solve local problems to gain their support and loyalty.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691750/extras/fc3de74277c6b7ebc36cc6bebb778aff.poster.avif?t=1760535466\" widt